    JiraConfig  
    JiraIssue
    An instance of this class represents a Jira issue, and the parser hooks needed to extract the data from the JSON event stream we use to parse it.

    An instance of this class represents a Jira JSON object, and the parser hooks needed to understand it.

    An instance of this class represents the results of a Jira query, and the ability to parse the corresponding JSON response.
